import { lazy } from 'react'
import { DEFAULT_PATHS } from 'config.js'


const appRoot = DEFAULT_PATHS.APP.endsWith('/') ? DEFAULT_PATHS.APP.slice(1, DEFAULT_PATHS.APP.length) : DEFAULT_PATHS.APP;

const home = lazy(() => import('views/home'))


const config = {
	address_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/address_type')),
	organization_status: lazy(() => import('views/config/organization_status')),
	organization_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/organization_type')),
	contact_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/contact_type')),
	phone_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/phone_type')),
	email_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/email_type')),
	document_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/document_type')),
	file_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/file_type')),
	logs: lazy(() => import('views/config/logs')),
}

const vehicles = {
	list: lazy(() => import('views/vehicles/list')),
	status: lazy(() => import('views/vehicles/status')),
	type: lazy(() => import('views/vehicles/type')),
}


const drivers = {
	list: lazy(() => import('views/drivers/list')),
	status: lazy(() => import('views/drivers/status')),
	type: lazy(() => import('views/drivers/type')),
}


const organizations = {
	list: lazy(() => import('views/organizations/list')),
	denied: lazy(() => import('views/organizations/denied')),
	users: lazy(() => import('views/organizations/users')),
}

const users = {
	list: lazy(() => import('views/users/list')),
	user_type: lazy(() => import('views/config/user_type')),
}



const orders = {
	list: lazy(() => import('views/orders/list')),
	status: lazy(() => import('views/orders/status')),
	type: lazy(() => import('views/orders/type')),
}

const routesAndMenuItems = {
	mainMenuItems: [
		{
			path: DEFAULT_PATHS.APP,
			exact: true,
			redirect: true,
			to: `${appRoot}/home`,
			protected: true
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/home`,
			component: home,
			label: 'Dashboard',
			icon: 'dashboard-1',
			protected: true
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/order`,
			component: orders.index,
			label: 'Ordens de coleta',
			icon: 'car',
			protected: true,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/list', label: 'Listar', component: orders.list },
				{ path: '/type', label: 'Tipo', component: orders.type },
				{ path: '/status', label: 'Status', component: orders.status },
			],
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/users`,
			component: users.index,
			label: 'Usuários',
			icon: 'user',
			protected: true,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/list', label: 'Listar', component: users.list },
				{ path: '/type', label: 'Tipo', component: users.user_type },
			],
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/organizations`,
			component: organizations.index,
			label: 'Empresas',
			icon: 'building-large',
			protected: true,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/list', label: 'Listar', component: organizations.list },
				{ path: '/import', label: 'Importação', component: organizations.denied },
				{ path: '/reports', label: 'Relatórios', component: organizations.reports },
				{ path: '/status', label: 'Status das empresas', component: config.organization_status },
				{ path: '/type', label: 'Tipo das empresas', component: config.organization_type },
				{ path: '/users', label: 'Usuários', component: organizations.users },
			],
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/drivers`,
			component: drivers.index,
			label: 'Motoristas',
			icon: 'navigate-diagonal',
			protected: true,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/list', label: 'Motoristas', component: drivers.list },
				{ path: '/status', label: 'Status dos motoristas', component: drivers.status },
				{ path: '/type', label: 'Tipo dos motoristas', component: drivers.type },
			],
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/vehicles`,
			component: vehicles.index,
			label: 'Veículos',
			icon: 'car',
			protected: true,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/list', label: 'Veículos', component: vehicles.list },
				{ path: '/status', label: 'Status dos Veículos', component: vehicles.status },
				{ path: '/type', label: 'Tipo dos Veículos', component: vehicles.type },
			],
		},

		{
			path: `${appRoot}/config`,
			component: config.index,
			label: 'Configurações',
			icon: 'gear',
			protected: true,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/activity_logs', label: 'Log de acessos', component: config.logs },
				{ path: '/params', label: 'Parâmetros do sistema', component: organizations.denied },
				{ path: '/address_type', label: 'Tipo de endereço', component: config.address_type },
				{ path: '/contact_type', label: 'Tipo de contato', component: config.contact_type },
				{ path: '/phone_type', label: 'Tipo de telefone', component: config.phone_type },
				{ path: '/email_type', label: 'Tipo de email', component: config.email_type },
				{ path: '/document_type', label: 'Tipo de documento', component: config.document_type },
				{ path: '/file_type', label: 'Tipo de arquivo', component: config.file_type },
			],
		},
	],
	sidebarItems: [
		{
			path: `${appRoot}/organizations`,
			component: organizations.index,
			label: 'Usuários',
			icon: 'users',
			protected: false,
			visible: false,
			subs: [
				{ path: '/users/:slug', label: 'Usuários', component: organizations.users },
			],
		},
	],
}

export default routesAndMenuItems
